Package: nhschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process New Hampshire School Enrollment Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school enrollment data for New Hampshire
    public schools. Data is sourced directly from the New Hampshire Department
    of Education (NH DOE) iPlatform reporting system. Provides functions for
    fetching enrollment data and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Includes district and school-level enrollment by grade. Historical data
    typically available for approximately 10 years.
